import ipaddress

def is_ip_in_range(ip, start_ip, end_ip):
    ip = ipaddress.ip_address(ip)
    start_ip = ipaddress.ip_address(start_ip)
    end_ip = ipaddress.ip_address(end_ip)

import ipaddress

def is_ip_in_range(ip, start_ip, end_ip):
    ip = ipaddress.ip_address(ip)
    start_ip = ipaddress.ip_address(start_ip)
    end_ip = ipaddress.ip_address(end_ip)
    return start_ip == ip <= end_ip
